      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i just cut my arm really bad while cooking. its a deep one and its still kinda oozing blood even after i put pressure on it for a bit. i dont really want to go to the hospital if i dont have to... do u think if i just put some honey on it and wrap it up tight with a bandage it'll be okay? i heard honey is good for healing stuff",
