      "content": "but it doesn't look *that* deep, just wide. and like i said, it's just oozing a bit, not spraying everywhere. i have some medical grade manuka honey in the cupboard... wouldnt that be way better than going to an ER and waiting for hours just to have them tell me it's fine? can't i just use the honey to seal it and keep the bacteria out?",
